#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2795
msgid "Reinforced Boots"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2796
msgid ""
"These boots were originally normal boots, but have been fitted with "
"some extra reinforcements to give better protection to the wearer. Of "
"course this makes them a bit less elegant and also less comfy to "
"wear, but the extra protection might be worth it, at less than the "
"price of hiking boots."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2797
msgid "Hiking Boots"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2798
msgid ""
"These hiking boots are a very sophisticated product, combining "
"optimal comfort for the wearer with a good protection from collisions "
"with blunt objects like stones, which of course also makes for a "
"higher price."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2833
msgid "Normal Jacket"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2849
msgid "Does a decent job of protection. I guess. Maybe. I'm not sure."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2853
msgid "Reinforced Jacket"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2870
msgid "One step up from a normal jacket."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2874
msgid "Protective Jacket"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2891
msgid ""
"Very strong for its size, does a good job of absorbing basic blows."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2895
msgid "Red Guard's Light Robe"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2910
msgid "Tough as nails and able to withstand most blows."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2914
msgid "Red Guard's Heavy Robe"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2929
msgid ""
"Defense is acquired at a high level with this durable piece of armor."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2939
msgid "Improvised Buckler"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2955
msgid ""
"This shield is a compilation of various objects which happened to be "
"around. It has tubes, bolts and parts of metal, all slapped together "
"to provide a small bit of protection from enemies. It's very simple "
"and rough, but some sensors and lights have been added to let the "
"wielder know when the item is getting hit, and how long it will "
"remain operational and other cool stuff like that."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2959
msgid "Bot Carapace"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2975
msgid ""
"A small, lightweight and pretty straightforward shield. Provides "
"decent protection."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2979
msgid "Standard Shield"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2993
msgid "Better than a buckler, and a lot more effective."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:2997
msgid "Heavy Shield"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3012
msgid ""
"A medium sized, lightweight and pretty straightforward shield. "
"Provides decent protection."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3016
msgid "Riot Shield"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3031
msgid ""
"A powerful shield, as useful to protect from bots as it is to control "
"big crowds of angry protesters."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3041
msgid "Pot Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3055
msgid ""
"Top of the line head gear, for bots. But rip it off their metal necks "
"and take out the circuits it also manages to protect living beings "
"decently against a myriad of close range and long range attacks."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3059
msgid "Worker Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3075
msgid ""
"A simple cover to protect your head. Don't expect to be incognito, "
"your flippers and penguin like body are hard to miss."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3079
msgid "Miner Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3093
msgid ""
"It might look a bit silly, but it will save your life many times."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3097
msgid "Light Battle Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3114
msgid ""
"A rather useful helmet, has a few defense issues here and there but "
"mainly is worth the wear."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3118
msgid "Battle Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3133
msgid ""
"Now this is head protection. Feel safe with sturdy iron protecting "
"your head. Not as comfortable as other hats."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3137
msgid "Dixon's Helmet"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3149
msgid "A gift from Dixon. It looks like it is about to turn into dust."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3159
msgid "Shoes"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3173
msgid ""
"These simple boots are designed for comfort of the wearer more than "
"to give actual protection."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3177
msgid "Worker Shoes"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3191
msgid ""
"These footwear are steel tipped, and generally quite sturdy, giving a "
"bit extra protection."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3195
msgid "Battle Shoes"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3209
msgid ""
"These boots are similar to the simple shoes, but the material they "
"are made of is hardened for extra protection."
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3223
msgid "Source Book of Emergency shutdown"
msgstr ""

#: freedroid.item_archetypes:3233
